<title>Groups of two 16th notes</title>
<tocimage>img222.png</tocimage>

<para>In this lesson the next patterns are introduced:</para>

<para><score width="600" height="100" border="0">
    <score_type>short</score_type>
    <control_play></control_play>
    <control_measures></control_measures>
    <music>
        (Metrica 2 8 NoVisible)(s c)(n * s g+)(n * s g-)(Barra Doble))
        (c (n * s g+)(n * s g-)(s c)(Barra Final))
    </music>
</score></para>

<part><title>Listen and take notice of the differences</title>

<para><score width="600" height="100" border="0">
    <score_type>short</score_type>
    <control_play></control_play>
    <control_measures></control_measures>
    <music>
        (Metrica 2 8)(s c)(n * s g+)(n * s g-))
        (c (n * s g+)(n * s g-)(s c)(Barra Final))
    </music>
</score></para>
</part>

